ceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"現在也是，覺得很恐怖所以不敢前進……\n像小亞，戶山同學那樣子……能夠有前進力量的人……\n如果他們不拉我一把……我可能連動都沒辦法動","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event76-07-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"燐子學姊……嗯，我倒覺得是香澄的前進力量太多了呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event76-07-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"呵呵……而且，只要一行動……\n冰川同學和松原同學，都會幫助我……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event76-07-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"如果沒有……像市谷同學一樣，可以……\n一起加油的人的話……\n我就會、馬上想要……逃離的……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event76-07-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx"